Van Heerden and FLA create a safe space in which stakeholders representing different interest groups within a global supply chain can work together to resolve conflicts of rights and interests, filling in the governance gap. Van Heerden&#39;s newest initiative: the Institute for Social and Environmental Responsibility, which will conduct research and convene multi-stakeholder forums on corporate responsibility.</p>"}],"speaker_name":"Auret van Heerden","tags":["big problems","business","global issues","inequality","law","work"],"title":"Making global labor fair","video_type":{"id":"1","name":"TED Stage Talk"},"viewed_count":614529}]}
